FBIS4-12985 "drnes073_l_94004" FBIS-NES-94-073 Daily Report 14 Apr 1994 ISRAEL Body of Perpetrator of Hadera Attack Identified Body of Perpetrator of Hadera Attack Identified TA1404144994 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el in Hebrew 1400 GMT 14 Apr 94 TA1404144994 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el Hebrew BFN [Text] The body of the terrorist who perpetrated the Hadera suicide attack has been identified. He was 23-year-old 'Ammar Salah 'Amarani from the Samaria village of Ya'bad. Our correspondent Moti Amir reports that the man was a known Hamas [Islamic Resistance Movement] activist, but he had been never detained by the security forces. Hamas has announced in a leaflet in Gaza that members of the 'Izz-al-Din al-Qassam squad carried out the Hadera attack in revenge for the Hebron massacre.
